🎬 CASTING CALL – STUDENT SHORT FILM (PAID)

From SFTV and director Madison Simmons comes Next, a dramedy short film exploring character-driven storytelling with heart and humor.

📅 Production Date: November 21st–23rd, 2025
📍 Location: Los Angeles, CA, USA
💰 Pay: $300 Flat (Lead Role)
🏷 Union Status: Non-Union
🎥 Poduction Company: SFTV Student Production

ABOUT THE PROJECT 
Next is a dramedy short film capturing a powerful moment in a man’s later life. Directed by Madison Simmons, this student-led production offers both a heartfelt script and the chance to collaborate with a passionate, up-and-coming creative team.

SEEKING TalentPlus🎭 Role: Male Lead (African-American)
📌 Age Range: 60–70
🧠 The character requires strong emotional depth and presence to bring this introspective story to life.

🎓 This is a fantastic opportunity for experienced or emerging older actors to gain lead credit in a meaningful, narrative-driven piece.

WHAT’S INCLUDED
🎞 Credit
🍽 Meals Provided
💵 $300 Flat Rate

📩 HOW TO APPLY:
🎭 Apply for this casting as a Talent PRO member at Actors and Extras with a 1-month FREE trial period.

👉 Visit [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)
Create your own FREE profile and GET NOTIFIED of castings in your area.

Join [www.actorsandextras.com](https://www.actorsandextras.com) today!

🔍 This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.

items.text:
I’m Majid Kamali, based in Burnaby, BC — a professional stunt performer and action coordinator, and a multi-time champion in motocross, stunt riding, car racing, and off-road driving.

My experience includes motorcycle and car stunts, fight choreography, high-altitude and rappel work, and safe fire stunts.

I have a fit, muscular, athletic build (177 cm / 68 kg) and a camera-friendly look. I can also perform on-camera acting roles, especially in action or physically demanding scenes.

🎬 Portfolio & demo clips:

https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1PPZ_mZ2RQ3Fd6oHuWB-h1sVmjvwdR_Rb

📧 majid64kamali@gmail.com

📞 236-660-6333

Excited to collaborate and bring safe, dynamic, and professional stunt work to your next project!

items.text:
Casting call!

We're so excited to be casting for our female-focused feature film, Before Us!

Log line: Five strangers wrestle with motherhood and identity while, unbeknownst to them, their great grandmothers meddle from the afterlife. As their stories increasingly intertwine, the women must discover purpose from within themselves and from one another.

Genre: Dramedy

Paid, non-union

This first casting call includes our leads and key supporting roles, each paying $500-$750 depending on the success of fundraising and the final shooting schedule. We plan to shoot a teaser trailer and some social media content for fundraising purposes in November, with principal photography in January-February 2026. You can see full character breakdowns and audition submission instructions here: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1mi16s2oN0Gdn0KYzpTw6VKL1LIG1mytkHOXYFYM_a3M/edit?pli=1

We're casting for:

Izzy: 30, female, Chamorro (While a Chamorro actress is ideal, Izzy can be played by any Pacific Islander)

Agnes: 51, female, Chinese-American (While a Chinese actress is ideal, Agnes can be played by any actor of East Asian descent)

Sasha: 36, female, Black

Beatrice: Any age 50 or older, female, Black

Leticia: Any age 50 or older, female, Latina

Mabel: Any age 50 or older, female, Chinese (While a Chinese actress is ideal, she can be played by any actor of East Asian descent)

Manåmko’: Any age 50 or older, female, Chamorro (While a Chamorro actress is ideal, she can be played by any Pacific Islander)

Margaret: Any age 50 or older, female, white

Foster: 29, male, any ethnicity

Please submit your audition via the form linked above by 11:59 pm on Saturday, November 1.

items.text:
New ROLE/S Added!!!!!

General ages 50-60 moderate supporting role filming Dec. 9th filming in CO springs 3-7 pm

Also we need a PA for a few days in November (Denver shoot) and some extras to be investigators and plain clothed cops (In Denver on Nov 12th 12-8ish)

Please send reels, headshots, resume to *daviskathy021@gmail.com*
Please send all correspondence to email. Thank you.
Will get a reel and IMDB credit.
